    'God reassures Moses and renews His promise. The genealogy of Moses and Aaron through Levi.',
    'The first plague: water turned to blood. The second plague: frogs cover the land.',
    'The third plague: lice. The fourth plague: swarms of flies. Pharaoh begins to negotiate but hardens his heart.',
    'The fifth plague: livestock disease. The sixth plague: boils. Pharaoh\'s heart remains hard.',
    'The seventh plague: hail destroys crops and livestock in the field. Pharaoh admits sin but hardens his heart again.',
    'The eighth plague: locusts devour everything the hail left. The ninth plague: three days of thick darkness over Egypt.',
