    'Jethro visits Moses. He advises Moses to appoint judges to help govern the people. Moses organizes a system of delegation.',
    'Israel arrives at Sinai. God descends on the mountain with thunder, lightning, and smoke. The people tremble. God speaks the Ten Commandments.',
